Fix: Skia Canvas circle disappears when returning to Details page

Problem:
- When entering Details page for the first time, Skia Canvas circles display normally
- When returning to Details page, Skia Canvas circles disappear
- Root cause: Pre-created RNInstance runs bundle in background without UI surface,
  causing Skia components to fail attaching when reused

Solution:
- Add forceReloadOnAppear flag to BasePrecreateView
- When forceReloadOnAppear=true, force re-run bundle even if pre-created instance exists
- This ensures React components re-mount and Skia components re-attach properly

